<br>
Immortal healing in pvp is mostly a problem when a non-evil team member attacks another non-evil team members because of the mentality that Vallon is &quot;supposed&quot; to be the 3 light teams vs the evil team.  So 3 team lights get very upset if you are a wood elf and come into a zone and start wasting humans and pecks.  Newsflash- Vallon Zek is not a roleplay server, it wasn't supposed to be 3 teams vs 1.<br>
<br>
Mostly Vallon has turned into a guild vs guild server for the high level game.  No one cares about the low level game anyways because the game isn't based for them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.thesafehouse.org/~fricka/shanks/teenyknot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/16/01 11:17:29 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/~fricka/sig/5fricka60x56.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> 4 Teams</span><hr size=1> &quot;The only high levels that quit...&quot; I wasn't talking about just the high levels I meant the entire server of which the majority is NOT high levels.<br>
<br>
You've already expressed that you don't care about players in any levels other than high, but to each their own game.  As for what VZ is &quot;supposed&quot; to be... no one can truly say. But for what it's worth I spoke to the dev team and the senior VZ guide (at the time) in person and they spoke about 4 team / pure team play.<br>
<br>
Roleplaying is also an individual's choice...or one of the several RP guilds on the server.  Even choosing to play &quot;light teams&quot; vs &quot;dark teams&quot; is a roleplay choice, though not one that I happen to agree with.<br>
<br>
At any rate, I'm presently having a grand time in another universe! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=509.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showMessage?topicID=506.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=505.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.threadControl?topicID=505.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=505.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=505.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesafehousefrm15">Th